      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;del&gt;啊啊啊，我不要上学啊&lt;/del&gt;，看看我在高一后的寒假里都做了点什么吧。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;重点-1满-16-周岁--备案完成&#34;&gt;重点 1：满 16 周岁 + 备案完成&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先重头戏的那肯定就是&lt;strong&gt;满 16 周岁&lt;/strong&gt;，所以在寒假期间我给我的域名整了&lt;strong&gt;icp 备案&lt;/strong&gt;以及&lt;strong&gt;公安备案&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/d67322d91698/af67b7c29851/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;320&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;174&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io